.git
.github
terraform
**/.DS_Store
# macOS AppleDouble resource forks ("._foo") — these are binary metadata files
# created when copying onto non-HFS+ filesystems. Symfony YAML treats them as
# YAML files and crashes on the binary header. Never ship them.
**/._*
**/node_modules
cms/storage/logs/*
cms/storage/runtime/*
cms/vendor
public_html/uploads/*
public_html/imager
public_html/cpresources
